reground transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a><button type=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" data-slot=\"button\" aria-label=\"Toggle theme\" class=\"group/button inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-transparent bg-clip-padding text-sm font-medium whitespace-nowrap transition-all outline-none select-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-3 focus-visible:ring-ring/50 active:translate-y-px disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 aria-invalid:border-destructive aria-invalid:ring-3 aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:border-destructive/50 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 [&amp;_svg:not([class*=&#x27;size-&#x27;])]:size-4 hover:bg-muted hover:text-foreground aria-expanded:bg-muted aria-expanded:text-foreground dark:hover:bg-muted/50 size-8\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sun size-4 scale-100 rotate-0 transition-all dark:scale-0 dark:-rotate-90\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M12 20v2\"></path><path d=\"m4.93 4.93 1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"m17.66 17.66 1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 12h2\"></path><path d=\"m6.34 17.66-1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"m19.07 4.93-1.41 1.41\"></path></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-moon absolute size-4 scale-0 rotate-90 transition-all dark:scale-100 dark:rotate-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20.985 12.486a9 9 0 1 1-9.473-9.472c.405-.022.617.46.402.803a6 6 0 0 0 8.268 8.268c.344-.215.825-.004.803.401\"></path></svg></button></div></div></nav><div class=\"flex flex-1 flex-col\"><main class=\"mx-auto w-full max-w-3xl flex-1 px-4 py-10 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Terms of Service\"}]}</script><nav aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\" class=\"mb-4\"><ol class=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right size-3.5 shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-foreground\">Terms of Service</span></li></ol></nav><h1 class=\"text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Terms of Service</h1><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Last updated: <!-- -->May 14, 2026</p><div class=\"mt-8 space-y-8 text-muted-foreground\"><section><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-foreground\">The short version</h2><p>Free Tool Shed&#x27;s tools are free to use for personal or commercial work, with no sign-up required. They are provided &quot;as-is,&quot; supported by display advertising, and may be changed or removed at any time. You retain ownership of any files you process; we never see or store them.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-foreground\">Permitted use</h2><p>You may use the tools for personal projects, commercial work, client deliverables, education, research, or any other lawful purpose. You do not need to attribute Free Tool Shed in outputs (e.g. invoices, resumes, exported audio) — they are yours to use however you want.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-foreground\">What you may not do</h2><ul class=\"mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6\"><li>Use the tools to produce content that infringes someone else&#x27;s copyright, trademark, or other rights.</li><li>Generate fraudulent documents — for example, falsified pay stubs or invoices intended to deceive a lender, employer, landlord, or government agency. The pay stub generator is for legitimate record-keeping; misuse is your responsibility, not ours.</li><li>Scrape, mirror, automate large-volume traffic against, or attempt to extract the tool source for redistribution under a different brand.</li><li>Use the tools to develop or train competing services without independent reimplementation.</li><li>Probe, scan, or attempt to compromise the site&#x27;s security or the integrity of other users&#x27; sessions. Security research is welcome — see the Contact page for how to report findings responsibly.</li></ul></section><section><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-foreground\">&quot;As-is&quot; disclaimer</h2><p>The tools are provided without warranties of any kind, express or implied. We do not guarantee that any tool will be available, uninterrupted, error-free, or fit for a specific purpose. Outputs (PDFs, exported audio, converted files, calculation results) should be reviewed before you rely on them — particularly for legal, financial, medical, or compliance use cases.</p><p class=\"mt-3\">The OCR scanner, periodic table calculations, unit conversions, and similar reference-style tools aim for accuracy but are not a substitute for professional verification when the stakes are high.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-foreground\">Limitation of liability</h2><p>To the maximum extent permitted by law, Free Tool Shed and its operator are not liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or punitive damages arising out of your use of the site or its tools — including loss of data, loss of business, or errors in generated documents. If a court finds we are liable despite this clause, our total liability is limited to the amount you paid us in the twelve months before the claim, which for a free ad-supported site is zero.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-foreground\">Your content</h2><p>Files you upload into a tool stay on your device. They are processed in your browser via WebAssembly or JavaScript, and never transmitted to our servers. You retain full ownership of your inputs and outputs. We claim no license to your files, your generated PDFs, or anything you create with the site.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-foreground\">Our content</h2><p>The site design, tool source code, written content (including SEO copy, FAQs, and tool guides), and Free Tool Shed branding are owned by the operator. You may not copy, mirror, or rebrand the site or its tools. Linking to individual tool pages is encouraged.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-foreground\">Advertising</h2><p>The site is supported by display advertising through Google AdSense. By using the tools, you acknowledge that ads will be shown alongside the tool workspace. Tool workspaces themselves are always ad-free. See the<!-- --> <a href=\"/privacy\" class=\"text-brand underline underline-offset-4\">Privacy Policy</a> <!-- -->for how advertising cookies are handled.</p><p class=\"mt-3\">We don&#x27;t run interstitials, popups, autoplay video ads, or anything that interferes with tool use. Ad blockers are tolerated; the tools work fine with them on.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-foreground\">Availability and changes</h2><p>Tools may be added, modified, removed, or temporarily unavailable without notice. We may rename URLs, change export formats, or retire tools that no longer make sense. If a tool you depend on is going away, we&#x27;ll try to flag it on the tool&#x27;s page in advance.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-foreground\">Changes to these terms</h2><p>We may update these terms over time. The &quot;Last updated&quot; date at the top of this page reflects the most recent change. Continued use of the site after a change constitutes acceptance of the revised terms. Material changes will be flagged on the homepage before they take effect.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-foreground\">Contact</h2><p>Questions about these terms? Email<!-- --> <a href=\"mailto:hello@freetoolshed.com\" class=\"text-brand underline underline-offset-4\">hello@freetoolshed.com</a>.</p></section></div></main><!--$--><!--/$--></div><footer class=\"border-t border-border bg-muted/40\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex max-w-7xl flex-col items-center gap-4 px-4 py-8 sm:flex-row sm:justify-between sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> Free Tool Shed. All rights reserved.</p><nav class=\"flex gap-4 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/privacy\">Privacy</a><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/terms\">Terms</a></nav></div></footer><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0eyplc079uusk.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[83661,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0zif8_3mgcc0x.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0zv.me6xdrdsz.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0ag6f0zogt0qg.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks