d pay stubs or invoices intended to deceive a lender, employer, landlord, or government agency. The pay stub generator is for legitimate record-keeping; misuse is your responsibility, not ours.\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Scrape, mirror, automate large-volume traffic against, or attempt to extract the tool source for redistribution under a different brand.\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Use the tools to develop or train competing services without independent reimplementation.\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Probe, scan, or attempt to compromise the site's security or the integrity of other users' sessions. Security research is welcome — see the Contact page for how to report findings responsibly.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-foreground\",\"children\":\"\\\"As-is\\\" disclaimer\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"The tools are provided without warranties of any kind, express or implied. We do not guarantee that any tool will be available, uninterrupted, error-free, or fit for a specific purpose. Outputs (PDFs, exported audio, converted files, calculation results) should be reviewed before you rely on them — particularly for legal, financial, medical, or compliance use cases.\"}],\"$L15\"]}],\"$L16\",\"$L17\",\"$L18\",\"$L19\",\"$L1a\",\"$L1b\",\"$L1c\"]}]]}],null,\"$L1d\"]}]\n1e:[]\nf:\"$W1e\"\n10:[\"$\",\"$1\",\"h\",{\"children\":[null,[\"$\",\"$L1f\",null,{\"children\":\"$L20\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"hidden\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L21\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$22\",null,{\"name\":\"Next.Metadata\",\"children\":\"$L23\"}]}]}],[\"$\",\"meta\",null,{\"name\":\"next-size-adjust\",\"content\":\"\"}]]}]\n12:[\"$\",\"link\",\"0\",{\"rel\":\"stylesheet\",\"href\":\"/_next/static/chunks/123doanyjnwwq.css\",\"precedence\":\"next\",\"crossOrigin\":\"$undefined\",\"nonce\":\"$undefined\"}]\n13:[\"$\",\"link\",\"1\",{\"rel\":\"stylesheet\",\"href\":\"